1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
Email / Lead Intake Automation in n8n.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,000
The workflow receives leads from Gmail or a manual webhook.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:16,000
Incoming email and webhook data are normalized into one shared structure.

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Gemini classifies the message and extracts structured JSON lead fields.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:28,000
If the LLM quota is unavailable, a local fallback classifier keeps the workflow running.

6
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:34,000
The Is Lead node routes only qualified leads to notification and logging steps.

7
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:41,000
Telegram receives a lead summary with contact details, intent, and priority.

8
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:48,000
Google Sheets logs the timestamp, name, email, phone, message, source, intent, and priority.

9
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:55,000
The final execution confirms a stable end-to-end lead intake automation.
